transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Viagra, this is Charles.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I want to cancel my prescription.

Speaker 1: Okay, can I have your phone number?

Speaker 2: 760-535-6165.

Speaker 1: Michael Cruz in Coronado, California.

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay, do you just not need the pills as often as every month?

Speaker 2: Because we can pause everything and let you finish what you got.

Speaker 1: No, well, why did you send them this time?

Speaker 2: I didn't ask for them to be sent.

Speaker 1: The refills do come monthly, unless if you request a change in that.

Speaker 2: We completely understand if you don't need them monthly.

Speaker 1: So I could pause everything from now until June,

Speaker 2: so that way you have some time to use what you've got and then order as needed.

Speaker 1: No, I'll call back if I want them.

Speaker 2: Okay, I haven't even tried them yet.

Speaker 1: So, yeah, just cancel them.

Speaker 2: All right, thank you.

Speaker 1: Yep, take care.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
